OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start, with sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers. Cloud increasing
OL,7,Ffrom the southwest, with rain moving
OL,8,Fnortheastwards across much of England,
OL,9,FWales and Northern Ireland. Best of
OL,10,Fthe brighter skies holding on across
OL,11,FScotland and northeast England. Mild
OL,12,Fand Breezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloud and rain will continue
OL,15,Fto move northeastwards across the rest
OL,16,Fof the UK through the evening and
OL,17,Fovernight. Turning increasingly murky,
OL,18,Fwith hill fog and drizzle. Mild and
OL,19,Fbreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
