OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cloudy and damp start.
OL,6,FSlowly brightening up across central
OL,7,Fand southern parts through the day,
OL,8,Fwith sunny spells developing here.
OL,9,FCloudy elsewhere, with further rain
OL,10,Fpossible at times. Mild.
